room_title: Escape room "Treasure Island" by TrappedKC in Kansas City
room_address: 618 SW 3rd St, Ste E Lee's Summit, MO 64063
room_description: There’s one man leading the mutiny, and as the loyal remnant you must find out who is leading the mutiny, warn the captain, and beat the others to the treasure before it’s too late. If you fail, you could be marooned, killed, or taken prisoner!
